																		Author&#039;s Note
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pedantique" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3118444); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3118444&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248677" alt="Pedantique" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3118444)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pedantique" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3118444); return false;" >Pedantique</a></span> <span class="odate time_1549500995 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">07 Feb 2019 00:56</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4144416">
									

<blockquote>
<p>I don’t know the truth<br />
I don’t know the way<br />
I don’t know what to think<br />
I don’t know what to say</p>
<p>But that’s alright<br />
Yeah, that’s OK<br />
I don’t know anything<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p>Andrew W.K., <em><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ygWKEQrJ1cE">I Don't Know Anything</a></em></p>
</div>
</blockquote>
<hr />
<p>Senselessness is the best defense against dangerous nonsense.</p>
<p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3938622); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3938622&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1549519822" alt="The Great Hippo" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3938622)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3938622); return false;">The Great Hippo</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1549519822" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;">A Random Day</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fieldstone" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1436137); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1436137&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1549519822" alt="fieldstone" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1436137)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fieldstone" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1436137); return false;">fieldstone</a></span> for feedback at various stages of the writing process.</p>

